<p>One more suggestion, I realized that the height of the app is much longer than the width, and we cannot adjust it. It&#8217;s not proportionate at all (on our screen display, the width is longer than the heigh, right?). It&#8217;s just my suggestion, and it&#8217;s still your call.&nbsp;</p>
